nodes.text: Imperial Entanglements is an expansion for the Star Wars Miniatures game by Wizards of the Coast. It focuses on characters from The Empire Strikes Back and Return of the Jedi with Expanded Universe characters from this era as well. It is the second set to feature 40 miniatures, instead of the previous standard of 60. It was released March 17, 2009. The booster cover art was done by Terese Nielsen.
Rarity denoted as follows: Common (C), Uncommon (U), Rare (R), Very Rare (VR)
